                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the Christening” (fols. 3r-47r)
 II)
                     Maṣḥafa ṭomār “Book of the Letter (from Heaven)” (fols. 47v-61v)
 III)
                     Śǝrʿāta faws manfasāwi “Order of Spiritual Medicine” (fols. 61v-67v),
                     unindentified
